#. <a class="sc" id="sc11"></a>
msgctxt "an6.62:11.1"
msgid ""
"Idha panāhaṃ, ānanda, ekaccaṃ puggalaṃ evaṃ cetasā ceto paricca pajānāmi:"
msgstr "When I’ve comprehended the mind of a person, I understand:"

