msgstr "Wouldn’t you know that those coals would grow, increase, and spread?”"

msgctxt "an6.62:11.9"
msgid "“Evaṃ, bhante”."
msgstr "“Yes, sir.”"

#. VAR: rattiyā paccūsasamayaṃ → rattiyā paccūsasamaye (s1-3) | rattipaccūsasamaye (mr)
msgctxt "an6.62:11.10"
msgid ""
"“Seyyathāpi vā panānanda, rattiyā paccūsasamayaṃ sūriye uggacchante, "
"jāneyyāsi tvaṃ, ānanda, andhakāro antaradhāyissati, āloko pātubhavissatī”ti?"
msgstr ""
"“Suppose it’s the crack of dawn and the sun is rising. Wouldn’t you know "
"that the dark will vanish and the light appear?”"

msgctxt "an6.62:11.11"
msgid "“Evaṃ, bhante”."
msgstr "“Yes, sir.”"

msgctxt "an6.62:11.12"
msgid ""
"“Seyyathāpi vā panānanda, abhido majjhanhike bhattakālasamaye, jāneyyāsi "
"tvaṃ, ānanda, andhakāro antarahito āloko pātubhūto”ti?"
msgstr ""
"“Or suppose that it’s nearly time for the midday meal. Wouldn’t you know "
"that the dark had vanished and the light appeared?”"

msgctxt "an6.62:11.13"
msgid "“Evaṃ, bhante”."
msgstr "“Yes, sir.”"

